name: western-portion-ikonos-and-landsat-etm-merge-satellite-imagery-for-carlsbad-caverns-national-pa
notes: IKONOS and Landsat ETM+ image merge for Carlsbad Caverns National Park, New Mexico. The image has a spatial resolution of 12 meters and is comprised of 11 layers. The image was used in the classification of the vegetation map for the park.
